[normal]Why has the policy objective not been achieved?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“A member of an LLP shall not be regarded for any purpose as employed by the LLP unless, 
[normal]if he and the other members were partners in a partnership, he would be regarded for that purpose as employed by the partnership.
[normal]”
