[normal]Our response concentrates on the disguised remuneration parts of the consultation rather than the hybrid LLP aspects of the new regime.  We have concerns about some
[normal] 
[normal]of the rules relating to the latter and we will be taking these up directly with HMRC.  We do not propose to deal with them in this document.
